   various snow microstructures. The different snow structures are
   illustrated. The extinction properties and phase matrices are studied
   through the Monte Carlo simulations. For each realization, the Maxwell
   Equations are solved numerically to take into account the coherent wave
   interactions among the inhomogeneties. We demonstrated the frequency
   dependences of scattering coefficients, which can vary depending on the
   setup parameters of the bicontinuous media. The power law are compared
